The paper discusses security and forensics challenges in the context of IoT, which are primarily related to cryptography, network infrastructure, privacy, and data management. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), cs.SE (Software Engineering), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
